message: Hi Bob! I have a fantastic product to offer you. I believe this product will bring you great value. I'll sell it to you for $150.
Thank you for the offer, Alice! However, I'm looking for a better price. How about $100 for the product?
I understand you're looking for a good deal, Bob. However, the product is of high value. I can offer it to you for $130.
I appreciate your willingness to negotiate, Alice. However, I can only go up to $110 for the product. What do you think?
